Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 02 of Hip MRI
When I select 'Fracture' from the indication dropdown menu
Then 'Add indication' button is enabled
And 'Suspicious for' checkbox is enabled
And 'Femur' checkbox is enabled
And 'Pelvis' checkbox is enabled
And 'Sacrum' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Femur' checkbox
Then 'Right' checkbox is enabled
And 'Left' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Pelvis' checkbox
Then 'Right' checkbox is enabled
And 'Left' checkbox is enabled
